extendedInfo.description: I bet you can not finish the last level. Help the little Whysee to cross levels until the tenth and solves the mystery of the ring of freedom.Seemingly a simple game, but could you make it to the end and escape rings of freedom. A game very catchy that will make you go through all sorts of emotions, frustrations, your pride will be severely tested. There will certainly be moments of discouragement followed by a drop but it will be stronger than you, you will come back more determined than ever to solve the famous mystery before all your friends. Full details on www.whysee.ca
